George Eads https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Eads 0 George Coleman Eads III (born March 1, 1967), is an American actor, known for his role as Nick Stokes on the CBS police drama CSI: Crime Scene Investigation. On November 25, 2014, it was announced that Eads would be leaving the show, which in any event was not renewed for the following season—meaning he only missed the series finale television movie, Immortality. He currently stars as Jack Dalton on the CBS action-adventure series MacGyver.
